t: "And We crossed/passed/passed through with Israel`s sons and daughters the sea , so Pharaoh and his soldiers/warriors followed them (with) transgression and violating/breaking until when the drowning/sinking caught up/overtook him , he said: \"I believed that He is, no God except who Israel`s descendants believed with Him, and I am from the Moslems/submitters"